How-To-Repeat: Try to automount a directory on a locally connected IP gateway; if it
works, make sure that the BIND system is returning the addresses in the
wrong order (for some reason, our nameservers cycle the two IP 
addresses of the gateway (131.215.131.77 and 131.215.78.1)
for hosts on 131.215.131.x but for the hosts on 131.215.78.x they 
always return the 131.215.78.1 address of the gateway first...)
